programme.desc: Hui Pui-ching sering diperlakukan secara kasar oleh suaminya yang kejam, Fan Pak-nan. Di sebuah pesta, Pui-ching bertemu dengan seorang pengusaha kaya bernama Ha Mon-hin dan keduanya pun saling tertarik.

programme.title: The Purple Shell
programme.desc: Hui Pui-ching is often ill-treated by her husband Fan Pak-nan, a cruel and uncouth man. At a party, Pui-ching meets rich and erudite businessman, Ha Mon-hin and they are mutually attracted.

programme.title: The Invincible Fist
programme.desc: Here Lo Lieh (future international star of King Boxer) plays a dedicated chief constable for Tsang Chou village, who falls in love with the blind daughter of a bandit who is wreaking havoc.

programme.title: Scandal
programme.desc: Saat berandalan Zhen dan sahabatnya Chia mengumpulkan bukti-bukti korupsi para pejabat, mereka menuntut untuk menjadi gubernur di negara itu.

programme.title: Scandal
programme.desc: As the roguish scamp Zhen and his best friend Chia collected proofs of corruption from the officials, they demanded to become the governor of the country.

programme.title: The Spirit Of The Sword
programme.desc: Ketua Klan Air terluka parah oleh seorang samurai pembunuh sesaat sebelum duel tahunan di Danau Taihu. Ia menugaskan saudaranya Bao Yu dalam perjalanan panjang untuk menemukan obat untuknya.

programme.title: The Spirit Of The Sword
programme.desc: Water Clan Chief is severely wounded by a samurai killer shortly before the annual duel at Taihu Lake. He sends his brother Bao Yu on a long journey to find an antidote for him.

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: A 28-year-old IT geek has only been in love once. Surprisingly, he ends up getting romantically involved with five different women this year and the one thing they have in common is that they all live in far flung areas of Hong Kong. After taking five intensive relationship courses within these 365 days, will he find “the-one”?

programme.title: Once Upon A Time In Hong Kong
programme.desc: Seorang sersan polisi bekerja sama dengan ketua geng untuk menghasilkan miliaran dolar dari uang suap. Persaingan antara orang baik dan jahat pun dimulai ketika seorang pengacara bergabung dengan temannya di ICAC.

programme.title: Once Upon A Time In Hong Kong
programme.desc: A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: Schemes In Antiques
programme.desc: Xu Yuan berhasil mengungkap suatu misteri kuno ketika sebuah barang antik akan dikembalikan ke Tiongkok. Ia pun segera memulai perjalanan nan berisiko untuk memulihkan reputasi keluarganya.

programme.title: Schemes In Antiques
programme.desc: When an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his family's reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: A Legend
programme.desc: Seorang arkeolog memperhatikan bahwa tekstur relik yang ditemukan selama penggalian gletser sangat mirip dengan liontin giok yang terlihat dalam salah satu mimpinya.

programme.title: A Legend
programme.desc: An archeologist noticed that the texture of the relics discovered during the excavation of a glacier closely resembled a jade pendant seen in one of his dreams.

programme.title: Reunion Dinner
programme.desc: Chao Yang and Zi Hong are soon to wed but both have not met the other's parents. When a client requests for a livestream of their reunion dinner to promote his products, it set the stage for their parents' first meeting. Estranged from his mother, Yang decides to rent a family for the dinner which results in a series of mishaps and hilarity.

programme.title: Enter The Fat Dragon
programme.desc: Donnie Yen plays a Hong Kong police officer who is highly skilled in martial arts but balloons to more than 200 pounds after his fiancé left him. His boss can only assign simple tasks to him like escorting a criminal to Japan, but can he complete it?

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Kepala inspektur di unit anti-narkotika tetap teguh pada prinsip-prinsipnya sebagai seorang polisi, mempertaruhkan segalanya untuk memerangi kegiatan yang berhubungan dengan narkoba dan menangkap para pengedar.

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: The chief inspector in the anti-narcotics unit remains steadfast in his police officer principles, risking all to combat drug-related activities and apprehend traffickers.

programme.title: Treasure Hunt
programme.desc: Peggy syuting iklan di sebuah pulau terpencil kala sekelompok pria yang membawa peta harta karun tengah berburu harta Dinasti Ming yang tersembunyi. Namun, peta tersebut dicuri oleh Star, penghuni pulau tersebut.

programme.title: Treasure Hunt
programme.desc: Peggy shoots an ad on a deserted island while some mysterious men with the treasure map are also there to hunt for the hidden Ming Dynasty treasures. However, the map is stolen by Star who lives on the island.

programme.title: My Blue Summer
programme.desc: Zhi has been secretly in love with Nan since she met him once as a child. After graduating high school, Zhi realizes that she and Nan are in the same university, where they get to know each other by chance and become close friends. However, Zhi is still too shy to express her love for Nan. Will this long-term crush finally turn into true love?

programme.title: I Still Remember
programme.desc: Chi is a property agent who leads an aimless and unfulfilling life until he reunites with his P.E. teacher, Wong, from primary school. Despite his illness, Wong insists on keeping his promise of completing a 10K marathon to his late wife. Inspired by Wong, Chi brings himself to his feet and finds the courage to cheer himself on!

programme.title: Let's Have A Baby
programme.desc: Sebuah kisah menarik tentang kerumitan dalam menciptakan anak, yang menampilkan penampilan komedi langka oleh Alex Man Chi Leung.

programme.title: Let's Have A Baby
programme.desc: Sebuah kisah menarik tentang kerumitan dalam menciptakan anak, yang menampilkan penampilan komedi langka oleh Alex Man Chi Leung.

programme.title: Let's Have A Baby
programme.desc: A charming tale of child-creating complications, featuring a rare comedic performance by Alex Man Chi-leung.

programme.title: Let's Have A Baby
programme.desc: A charming tale of child-creating complications, featuring a rare comedic performance by Alex Man Chi-leung.

programme.title: Distinction
programme.desc: A music teacher in a special needs school, an underachiever from an elite school, and a rebellious teenager with a handicapped brother take part in a campus musical for various reasons. Little did they know that this turns out to be a journey of self-discovery.

programme.title: Man On The Edge
programme.desc: Ah Lok ditugaskan untuk menangani bisnis peredaran narkoba oleh pemimpin geng triad. Namun ternyata, ia merupakan seorang polisi yang berhasil membongkar suatu konspirasi politik nan mengejutkan selama penyelidikan.

programme.title: Man On The Edge
programme.desc: The triad gang leader assigns Ah Lok to take charge of the drug trafficking business. However, Ah Lok turns out to be an undercover police officer who unveils a shocking political conspiracy during the investigation.

programme.title: Only Cloud Knows
programme.desc: Berdasarkan kisah nyata sepasang suami istri, film ini bercerita tentang perjalanan seorang suami melintasi kampung halaman mereka di Selandia Baru menuju sejumlah tempat yang bermakna bagi mendiang istri tercintanya.

programme.title: Only Cloud Knows
programme.desc: This romantic drama is based on the story of a real-life couple. It follows a grieving husband as he journeys to places of significance to his beloved dead wife across their New Zealand homeland.

programme.title: Napping Kid
programme.desc: Analisis keuangan Xiao Ru untuk seorang klien bank dicuri secara daring. Uang tebusan pun harus dibayar dalam waktu tiga hari, jika tidak dokumen tersebut akan dipublikasikan.

programme.title: Napping Kid
programme.desc: Xiao Ru's financial analysis for a bank client was stolen online. A ransom has to be paid within three days or else the document would be disclosed.

programme.title: Twilight Of Warriors: Walled In
programme.desc: Mengikuti pemuda bermasalah Chan Lok-kwun saat dia secara tidak sengaja memasuki Kota Bertembok, menemukan keteraturan di tengah kekacauan, dan mempelajari pelajaran hidup yang penting di sepanjang jalan.

programme.title: Twilight Of Warriors: Walled In
programme.desc: Follows troubled youth Chan Lok-kwun as he accidentally enters the Walled City, discovers the order amidst its chaos, and learns important life lessons along the way.

programme.title: The Captain
programme.desc: The movie is based on a real incident of Sichuan Airlines Flight 8633 on 14 May 2018. When the cockpit windshield shatters after takeoff, the Captain manages to land the airplane safely with his level-headed swift actions and sheer determination. This is lauded as a miracle in airline history.

programme.title: Europe Raiders
programme.desc: Mr Lin and Miss Wang are the two top bounty hunters in the business, and are searching for the destructive missile “Hand of God” to prove who is the better bounty hunter. They soon realize they are not the only ones after the missile. Will Lin and Wang put their differences aside and work together in search for the ‘Hand of God’?

programme.title: Raging Fire
programme.desc: Sekelompok penjahat mencuri narkoba saat polisi hampir menangkap sang bandar. Inspektur Bong menemukan bahwa mereka dipimpin oleh Ngo, seorang mantan polisi yang terpaksa menjalani kehidupan kriminal karena dirinya.

programme.title: Raging Fire
programme.desc: As the police sets to arrest a drug lord, a team of masked thugs steals the drugs. Inspector Bong discovers that the killers are led by Ngo, a former fellow cop who was forced into a life of crime by him.

programme.title: Band Four
programme.desc: Seorang vokalis dari band indi bernama Band Four bertemu kembali dengan ayahnya yang seorang gitaris usai sepeninggalan sang ibu. Keduanya pun saling mendukung melalui kecintaan dan kegemaran mereka terhadap musik.

programme.title: Band Four
programme.desc: An aspiring singer of an indie band called Band Four reunites with her estranged guitarist father following the death of her mother. Together, they support each other through their love and passion for music.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs 3
programme.desc: 10 bulan setelah Yan terbunuh, Ming dipindahkan untuk bekerja di bagian administrasi. Sementara itu, seorang bintang baru, Wing muncul di kepolisian. Ming mencurigainya sebagai mata-mata yang diutus oleh triad.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs 3
programme.desc: 10 months after the murder of Yan, Ming is transferred to do the office work. Meanwhile, a new star Wing has emerged in the police force. Ming suspects he is also a mole sent by the triad.

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: Sebelum benar-benar menikah, seorang wanita Hong Kong yang baru bertunangan mencoba melepaskan diri dari sebuah pernikahan palsu rahasia dengan seorang pria yang membayarnya bertahun-tahun lalu.

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real.

programme.title: Cherie
programme.desc: A rich old man and a sexy young photographer compete for a stunning young gym instructor. The younger man is clearly winning until the rich man offers a deal.

programme.title: Cherie
programme.desc: A rich old man and a sexy young photographer compete for a stunning young gym instructor. The younger man is clearly winning until the rich man offers a deal.

programme.title: Mad Fate
programme.desc: A Master fortune teller predicts that Tung, a born psychopath, will be imprisoned for murder and tries to change his fate. A veteran detective believes Tung is a psychopathic serial killer after witnessing him kill a cat, and pursues him relentlessly. Can the Master change Tung’s mad fate?

programme.title: My Indian Boyfriend
programme.desc: Kisah asmara antara seorang gadis Hong Kong dan pemuda India, sekaligus merangkum sejumlah konflik diskriminasi, perbedaan latar belakang sosial budaya, gaya hidup, dan nilai-nilai keluarga antarras.

programme.title: My Indian Boyfriend
programme.desc: A love story between a Hong Kong girl and an Indian boy. It encapsulates the conflicts caused by discrimination as well as differences in social-cultural background, lifestyle and family values between the races.

programme.title: Endless Battle
programme.desc: Sepasang kakak beradik terlibat dalam perebutan wilayah kartel narkoba. Saat menjalankan misi pengawalan, sang kakak menemukan identitas rahasia adiknya hingga memunculkan persaingan antara kebaikan dan kejahatan.

programme.title: Endless Battle
programme.desc: This is a story about two brothers. Both are involved in a drug cartel¿s turf battle and during an escort mission, Zhong discovers his brother¿s hidden identity. This leads to an endless battle between good and evil.

programme.title: Flirting Scholar 2
programme.desc: The movie tells the story of Tang Bo Hu and his three buddies before they become the four great talents in Jiangnan. Tang Bo Hu encounters a beautiful girl when studying in a monastery and they quickly fall in love, but her hidden identity is accidentally unveiled when Tang and friends uncover a conspiracy at the monastery.

programme.title: The White Storm 3: Heaven Or...
programme.desc: An undercover cop who invade a drug cartel led by a notorious Thai drug lord. In classic heroic bloodshed fashion, the two develop a bond of brotherhood.

programme.title: Everything Is Unknown
programme.desc: Pan Yi Ming receives his father's will stating that he must attend his funeral at home to claim the huge inheritance. When he returns home, he encounters his ex-girlfriend, her husband Hua Qi and his daughter whom he has never met.

programme.title: Somewhere Winter
programme.desc: Film ini menampilkan kisah cinta seorang mahasiswa bernama An Ran dan seorang pria Taiwan, Qi Xiao. Mereka bertemu dan saling jatuh cinta di Beijing pada tahun 1991, di konser Chyi Chin, seorang penyanyi Taiwan.

programme.title: Somewhere Winter
programme.desc: The film follows the love story of a university student, An Ran and a Taiwanese man, Qi Xiao. They met and fell in love with each other in Beijing in 1991, at a concert by Chyi Chin, a Taiwanese singer.

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as "Magic Hands" Ken, a legendary gambling maestro who is forced out of retirement when his daughter's safety is compromised by an international gambling mafia. In order to save her, Ken and his new protégé Cool must work together to expose the evil mastermind by challenging him to a high stakes head-to-head battle of cards.

programme.title: Those Were The Days
programme.desc: Director Wong despises Cantonese movies of the 60s, but accidentally travels back in time to that movie set. He meets Director Chu, who tells him he can return to modern time if someone likes the film he makes. Wong meets four classic movie stars and invites them to star in his new film, but it flops unexpectedly. Can Wong return to the present?

programme.title: The Moon Thieves
programme.desc: Two young men become involved in a complicated crime involving antique watches.

programme.title: The Italian Recipe
programme.desc: Idola pop terkenal, Peng, pergi ke Roma untuk syuting reality show dan bertemu dengan seorang gadis, Mang, yang bercita-cita menjadi koki nan hebat di Italia. Hidup mereka pun berubah saat keduanya mulai jatuh cinta.

programme.title: The Italian Recipe
programme.desc: Famous pop idol Peng travels to Rome for a reality show and encounters an ordinary girl, Mang, who dreams of becoming a great chef after migrating to Italy. Their lives begin to change as the two start to fall in love.

programme.title: Binding Souls
programme.desc: Film ini berkisah tentang lima teman lama yang mengunjungi sekolah mereka sebelum akhirnya ditutup. Mereka gembira saat menemukan sejarah kejadian paranormal karena sekolah itu sebelumnya ditempati oleh warga Jepang.

programme.title: Binding Souls
programme.desc: The film talks about five old friends revisiting their school before it closes down. They were excited to find records of paranormal existence as the school was previously occupied by the Japanese.

programme.title: Social Distancing
programme.desc: Cherry mengalami sejumlah peristiwa nan misterius usai melihat sebuah video peringatan tentang 'e-ghost' di YouTube. Ia harus menghadapi masa lalunya nan kelam untuk keluar dari dunia paranormal yang mengerikan itu.

programme.title: Social Distancing
programme.desc: After seeing a warning video about an 'e-ghost' on YouTube, Cherry begins to encounter many mysterious incidents. She must face her unbearable past in order to get out of this horrifying paranormal world.

programme.title: Sinema Pagi
programme.desc: Menceritakan kisah penyelidikan kasus konspirasi yang dilakukan oleh Jack Reacher (Tom Cruise). Jack mendapat tugas untuk mencari tahu kasus yang menimpa Mayor Susan Turner (Cobie Smulders) yang ditangkap tanpa alasan yang jelas. Susan ditangkap oleh polisi militer terkait kasus kematian dua orang anak buahnya yang bertugas di Timur Tengah. Jack pun berusaha membantu Susan dan mencari tahu kebenaran di balik kasus ini. Namun, saat dirinya sedang disibukkan oleh kasus Mayor Susan, tiba-tiba ada seorang wanita membawa seirang anak bernama Samantha (Danika Yarosh). Wanita tersebut menuntut tunjangan dari Jack dan mengatakan bahwa Samantha adalah anaknya. Jack yang merasa bingung dan ragu pun mencoba mencari tahu apakah Samantha benar-benar anaknya. Sayangnya, Samantha harus terseret ke keadaan berbahaya karena penyelidikan yang dilakukan oleh Jack.
